---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HeaderComponent from "../components/HeaderComponent.astro";
import PageTitleComponent from "../components/PageTitleComponent.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="🛠️ 更新日志">

    <HeaderComponent />

    <PageTitleComponent title="🛠️ 更新日志" />
    
    <!-- =====更新日志===== -->
    <section class="container mx-auto pt-16">
        <ol class="relative border-s border-black/10 leading-loose font-mono tracking-wide"> 
            <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
                <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-sky-500 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5"></div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm text-gray-500">开发中...</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">V2.1</h3>
                <article class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 pt-2.5 space-y-1">
                    <p><span class="bg-red-500 text-white text-xs px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full mr-2.5">问题</span>明暗主题未适配</p>
                    <p><span class="bg-orange-500 text-white text-xs px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full mr-2.5">计划</span>添加友链页面</p>
                    <p><span class="bg-green-500 text-white text-xs px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full mr-2.5">新增</span>Giscus 评论组件</p>
                </article>
            </li>       
            <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
                <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 mt-1.5 -start-1.5">
                    <span class="relative flex">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-green-500"></span>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm text-gray-500">2024-06-10</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">V2.0</h3>
                <article class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 pt-2.5 space-y-1">
                    <p>使用 Astro 框架重写，延续上个版本风格, 继续使用 Tailwindcss</p>
                    <p>新建了 Git 仓库，用 Vercel 重定向太多打不开部署多次失败，还是继续用Cloudflare Page</p>
                    <p><img class="w-full border border-black/25" src="/img/v2-0.png" alt="v2.0"></p>
                </article>
            </li>                 
            <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
                <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5"></div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm text-gray-500">2023-11-30</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">V1.2</h3>
                <article class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 pt-2.5 space-y-1">
                    <p>这次使用 daisyUI 组件库， 11月 30日 重构完成</p>
                    <p><img class="w-full border border-black/25" src="/img/v1-2.png" alt="v1.2"></p>
                </article>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
                <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5"></div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm text-gray-500">2023</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">V1.0</h3>
                <article class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 pt-2.5 space-y-1">
                    <p>通过引入 Tailwindcss CDN 方式，经过两次重构</p>
                </article>
            </li>
            <li class="ms-4">
                <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5"></div>
                <time class="mb-1 text-sm text-gray-500">2022</time>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">V0.1</h3>
                <article class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 pt-2.5 space-y-1">
                    <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">用引入 Bootcss CDN 方式写第一个单页版本，部署在Cloudflare Page</p>
                </article>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
